channel.title: 317 Remake ( New Project )
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i50.tinypic.com/4ptt7b.jpg[/img][/center]
[left][size=18pt][u]Information:[/u][/size][/left] This server will be based on the 317 - 377 version of RuneScape. This server will be mostly based on the ftp maps. This server will contain no custom items besides runescape items that were in the 317 - 377 version of RuneScape. I will try my best to keep the server very neat and clean. Most of the packets will be remade. This server will contain a plain 317 deob for the client. The Client will not contain alot of major updates besides interfaces. The client will have a 317 look and the base for the client will be pablos deob. Also im not sure if im gona have 420 interfaces yet, but thats all i would have no 474 etc. [b]* Please do not post unless you have something good to say.[/b]
[left][size=18pt][u]Server updates:[/u][/size][/left]
1. Added how many slots in inventory added. ( 100% perfect )( 1/15/09
[left][size=18pt][u]Client updates:[/u][/size][/left]
1. Made the Client load a full perfect 377 cache. ( 1/15/09 )
